data.description: Welcome to this stunning ranch home in Milwaukee! The main floor features a fully updated eat in kitchen and with beautiful tile floor, newer stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, new cabinets & a breakfast bar opening into the large living room still giving you an open concept feeling. The large windows keep this home full of natural light. All 3 bedrooms are spacious recently refinished hardwood floors, new lighting & generous sized closets. Newer central air unit (2022) and the large rec-room  has lots of space to entertain along with a bonus room on the lower level as well. The backyard is setup to enjoy BBQ's with family and friends.  An added bonus is a shed to store lawn and garden equipment without taking up space in the garage.
